text: Kargala () is a rural locality (a village) in Surensky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 186 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 54 km from Isyangulovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Kargala, Republic of Bashkortostan
